[TestInjectDiagnosticsTrimmed/short_line_below_threshold - 1]
without trimming:
2 | expr: foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar)
          ^^^
          foo() is deprecated
with trimming:
2 | expr: foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar) + foo(bar)
          ^^^
          foo() is deprecated

